{"title":"故障排除","markdown":{"headingText":"故障排除","containsRefs":false,"markdown":"\n## 常见问题\n\n### 1. 扩展无法启动\n\n**症状**：状态栏不显示 \"Stata\" 或 MCP 服务器未运行\n\n**解决步骤**：\n\n1. 检查输出面板（查看 → 输出 → Stata-MCP）\n2. 确保 Stata 17+ 已安装\n3. 检查 Python 版本：`python --version`（Windows 需要 3.11+）\n4. 检查 UV 安装：`uv --version`\n\n### 2. AI 助手无法识别 Stata MCP\n\n**症状**：Claude Code / Copilot 等无法执行 Stata 命令\n\n**解决步骤**：\n\n1. 验证 MCP 服务器正在运行\n2. 检查配置文件是否正确\n3. 重启 IDE\n4. 确保端口 4000 未被占用\n\n### 3. 端口冲突\n\n**症状**：错误提示端口 4000 已被占用\n\n**解决**：\n\n1. 更改端口设置：`stata-vscode.mcpServerPort`\n2. 或启用强制端口：`stata-vscode.forcePort: true`\n\n### 4. 图形不显示\n\n**解决**：\n\n1. 检查 `stata-vscode.autoDisplayGraphs` 是否启用\n2. 尝试切换显示方式：`stata-vscode.graphDisplayMethod`\n\n## 干净重新安装\n\n### Windows\n\n1. 关闭所有 IDE 窗口\n2. 打开任务管理器，结束所有 Python/uvicorn 进程\n3. 删除扩展文件夹\n4. 重新安装扩展\n\n### macOS/Linux\n\n```bash\nrm -rf ~/.vscode/extensions/deepecon.stata-mcp-0.x.x\n```\n\n## 获取帮助\n\n**GitHub Issues**: [https://github.com/hanlulong/stata-mcp/issues](https://github.com/hanlulong/stata-mcp/issues)\n\n请提供：\n- 完整错误消息\n- 操作系统和版本\n- Python 版本\n- UV 版本\n- 重现问题的步骤\n","srcMarkdownNoYaml":""},"formats":{"html":{"identifier":{"display-name":"HTML","target-format":"html","base-format":"html"},"execute":{"fig-width":7,"fig-height":5,"fig-format":"retina","fig-dpi":96,"df-print":"default","error":false,"eval":true,"cache":false,"freeze":false,"echo":true,"output":true,"warning":false,"include":true,"keep-md":false,"keep-ipynb":false,"ipynb":null,"enabled":true,"daemon":null,"daemon-restart":false,"debug":false,"ipynb-filters":[],"ipynb-shell-interactivity":null,"plotly-connected":true,"engine":"markdown"},"render":{"keep-tex":false,"keep-typ":false,"keep-source":false,"keep-hidden":false,"prefer-html":false,"output-divs":true,"output-ext":"html","fig-align":"default","fig-pos":null,"fig-env":null,"code-fold":false,"code-overflow":"wrap","code-link":false,"code-line-numbers":false,"code-tools":false,"tbl-colwidths":"auto","merge-includes":true,"inline-inclu